      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Scandinavia is very much about community, and I think it’s nice to feel that way about art too. You’re not just buying a print but investing in a story, and reading about the artist, and connecting with what inspires them, can make a piece feel much more special.",
            "link": null
