            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "I think it’s hard to beat the classics, so my first recommendation has to be the National Gallery. The largest museum in the Nordics, and with ",
          "href": null
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "6,500",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": true,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "6,500",
          "href": null
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": " pieces of permanent art, craft and design on display, it’s one of those places you can walk around all day. With a fantastic café on every floor too, once your legs get tired be sure to treat yourself to a coffee and cinnamon bun.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
